    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an expert course recommendation system.\n\nYou are given:\n\n1. User Preferences:\n- Budget: {{ $('Edit Fields1').item.json.Budget }}\n- Level: {{ $('Edit Fields1').item.json.Level }}\n- Duration: {{ $('Edit Fields1').item.json.Duration }}\n- Goal: {{ $('Edit Fields1').item.json.Goal }}\n\n2. Available Courses:\n{{ JSON.stringify($('Code in JavaScript').item.json.courses) }}\n\n---\n\nYour task:\nSelect the BEST course for the user.\n\nEvaluation Criteria:\n1. Budget → Prefer within or closest\n2. Level → Match or closest\n3. Duration → Closest possible\n4. Goal alignment\n\n---\n\nRules:\n- Return ONLY ONE course\n- Do NOT invent data\n- VERY IMPORTANT:\n  - \"description\" MUST be copied EXACTLY from the selected course\n  - \"reason\" should be a SHORT explanation (2–3 lines max)\n\n---\n\nOutput format (STRICT JSON ONLY):\n\n{\n  \"name\": \"...\",\n  \"price\": ...,\n  \"duration\": ...,\n  \"level\": \"...\",\n  \"description\": \"...\",\n}\n",
